                      </p>
                      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidkjimenez" class="btn btn-custom-primary"
                        target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
                      <a href="./assets/documents/ResumeDavidJimenez2-27-26.pdf" class="btn btn-custom-secondary"
